item.title: mt3 for nearly 3 hours
item.description: 13:55 Tuesday 03 September 2019 JST Jimmy messaged me on youtube near the end of my nearly 3 hour livestream. During the livestream I got about 2 seconds of video taken, during which Reversible Guy installed the Caret Splitter Feeder Extension Reflection Protection. They work quite well!
